data.description: Timeless elegance meets modern amenities in this spacious 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath Dutch Colonial home. Sitting on a beautiful corner lot with massive 2+ stall attached garage this home has TONS of character! Enter your gorgeous foyer with original French doors to both the formal living room on the left and dining room to the right. Living room features a fireplace and access to totally enclosed sunroom. Let your eyes feast on the original woodwork and hard wood flooring. Updated kitchen features stainless steel appliances, brand new microwave, and skylight. Main floor half bath, family room and laundry room complete your home needs. Second floor has full bath with updates, 3 large bedrooms and separate office area. Lots of fun to be had in the lofted bunk bedroom. Basement features 3/4 bath and room for your designing imagination to run wild. Add a bedroom, add a family room. Possibilities are endless! Home has newer windows for energy efficiency and ease of care with vinyl siding. This is the ONE you've been waiting for! It's time to come HOME!
